        <h2 data-key="about_page_title">About Us - Rashtriya Manav Adhikar Sangathan</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
            <p data-key="about_intro_p1">Founded in 2020, Rashtriya Manav Adhikar Sangathan (RMAS) is a registered organization dedicated to the promotion and protection of human rights across India. Guided by the principles of the Human Rights (Amendment) Act, 2006, we are committed to ensuring justice, equality, and dignity for every individual.</p>
            <p data-key="about_intro_p2">Our mission is to support the marginalized, raise awareness of rights violations, and build a society where every voice is respected. Through community outreach, legal aid, awareness campaigns, and collaboration with partners, we address critical issues such as discrimination, social injustice, and inequality.</p>

            <h3 data-key="about_vision_title">Our Vision</h3>
            <p data-key="about_vision_text">A just and inclusive society where human rights are universally respected and protected.</p>

            <h3 data-key="about_objectives_title">Our Objectives</h3>
            <ul>
                <li data-key="about_objective1">Promote awareness of human rights under the Human Rights (Amendment) Act, 2006.</li>
                <li data-key="about_objective2">Provide legal and moral support to victims of rights violations.</li>
                <li data-key="about_objective3">Collaborate with national and international organizations to strengthen rights frameworks.</li>
                <li data-key="about_objective4">Empower communities through education and advocacy.</li>
            </ul>

            <p data-key="about_conclusion">Since our inception, RMAS has been driven by compassion, integrity, and justice. We invite you to join our movement to create a future where every person can live with dignity and freedom.</p>
